name: CI Europe Hedged Equity Index ETF
longDescription: The investment objective of the CI WisdomTree Europe Hedged Equity Index ETF (the Fund) is to track, to the extent possible, the price and yield performance of the WisdomTree Europe CAD-Hedged Equity Index (the Benchmark or the Index), before fees and expenses. The investment strategy of the Fund is to invest in and hold a proportionate share of the constituent securities of the Index, or other securities, to track the price and yield performance of the Index. The Fund uses derivative instruments to hedge the foreign currency exposure of the securities attributable to the Hedged Units to the Canadian dollar.
